---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - UtilityHub" theme="night">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About UtilityHub</h1>
    
    <div class="max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-4">
        Welcome to UtilityHub, your one-stop destination for free, privacy-focused web utilities. Our platform hosts a collection of useful web applications designed to make your online tasks easier and more efficient.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We believe in creating simple, effective tools that respect user privacy. All our applications run directly in your browser without collecting or storing any personal data. Our commitment is to provide practical solutions while maintaining the highest standards of privacy and security.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Tools</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Each tool in our collection is designed with specific purposes in mind, from data conversion to calculation utilities. We continuously work to expand our collection and improve existing tools based on user feedback and needs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Privacy First</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We take pride in our no-tracking, no-data-collection approach. All operations are performed locally in your browser, ensuring your data remains private and secure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>